{"tid":1357920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於對罷工既共識","createTime":"2019-07-23T22:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T23:11:16.000Z","uid":242805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36b3d5cb7b8148ec4aa3e6e54215739ef5e847e5","tid":1357920,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:50:57.000Z","msg":"到底如何無大台發動罷工？<br />\n<br />\n因為所有大公司都沒反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假如差佬真係罷工，我地可以用人身安全爲由唔返？<br />\n<br />\n又或者港府真係宣布有恐襲，我地真係可以用人身安全爲由唔返<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁做既話，真係一石激起千層浪啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da3f086db78b7c35a07586b47679713034f6caa","tid":1357920,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:53:43.000Z","msg":"阻一阻你<br />\n<br />\n27號元朗反三黑 將會係爭取香港民主最重要既一日 簡而言之：勿 衝 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357808</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99c5a0ea13c73fb9861a9f17683cd4980280c094","tid":1357920,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:55:41.000Z","msg":"721 警員驅趕記者，向橋下的示威者發射橡膠子彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef3be73e256c06920173999673583b00740e978e","tid":1357920,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:01:46.000Z","msg":"仲有mtr,無共識搞黎做乜"},{"pid":"d31f33bddbf28703657b839598851a22be10882e","tid":1357920,"uid":242805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef3be73e256c06920173999673583b00740e978e","tid":1357920,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:01:46.000Z","msg":"仲有mtr,無共識搞黎做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:11:16.000Z","msg":"呢個都岩既，但係基於各有各做既原則，唔理果邊住先<br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果黑警頂唔住罷工<br />\n<br />\n即刻黎個全民罷工真係有得諗<br />\n<br />\n因為沒大型機構做第一步，所以沒人夠擔帶頭<br />\n<br />\n唔係請一日假咁簡單，係同公司講因爲有人身安全或者社會問題，所以係件事解決之前都唔會返"}]}